{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji8","name":"毛泽东全集第8卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji8.pdf"],"article":{"title":"稳固山西抗日根基","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"稳固山西抗日根基川"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年3月12日）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了推动全国抗日高潮，红军要迅速东进，奔赴抗日前线，坚决消灭一切阻拦前进的反动分子，同时要猛烈地扩大红军，扩大根据地，广泛发动群众，让抗日种子在山西扎根。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]1936年3月12日，毛泽东在郭家掌主持召开红一和红十五军团领"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1936,"month":3,"day":12}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":323,"page_end":323},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}